
### display:flex

1. [Flex 布局教程：语法篇](http://www.ruanyifeng.com/blog/2015/07/flex-grammar.html)
2. [Flex布局bug列表](https://github.com/philipwalton/flexbugs#9-some-html-elements-cant-be-flex-containers)


  .container{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center | space-between;  //水平方向的位置排列
    align-items： flex-start | flex-end | center; // 竖直方向的位置排列
  }
